# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ARCOLAB 5S Insight — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to: .env
#    (cp .env.example .env)
#
# 2. Fill in your own Supabase project values below.
#    You can find them at: https://supabase.com/dashboard → your project → Settings → API
#
# 3. NEVER commit the real .env file to Git. (It is already in .gitignore)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Your Supabase project reference ID (found in Settings → General)
VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID="your-project-ref-id"

# Your Supabase anon/public key (found in Settings → API → Project API Keys)
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="your-supabase-anon-key"

# Your Supabase project URL (found in Settings → API → Project URL)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL="https://your-project-ref-id.supabase.co"
